WEBVTT

00:02:25.778 --> 00:02:30.544
The word "kufungisisa"
opens up a floodgate of tears.

00:02:32.497 --> 00:02:36.753
So, kufungisisa is the local
equivalent of depression

00:02:36.777 --> 00:02:37.927
in my country.

00:02:38.776 --> 00:02:40.363
It literally means

00:02:40.837 --> 00:02:42.579
"thinking too much."

00:02:44.035 --> 00:02:47.444
The World Health Organization estimates

00:02:47.468 --> 00:02:53.577
that more than 300 million people
globally, today, suffer from depression,

00:02:53.601 --> 00:02:56.473
or what in my country
we call kufungisisa.

